@startuml
title US03 - SSD - View available appointment slots for a physician

autoactivate on
autonumber

actor "Patient"
participant ":RestAPI" as System
activate Patient

Patient -> System : GET /api/appointments/physicians/{id}/slots?start=YYYY-MM-DD

System --> Patient : 200 OK

deactivate Patient
note right of System
- Returns available appointment slots for the selected physician.
- Applies default slot duration and 5-minute intervals.
- Shows slots for the requested day and the next 10 days (max 3 months ahead).
end note
@enduml
